data.description: This beautifully rehabbed 4 bedroom (3 up & 1 down).  Great for a growing family. This home is overflowing with tons of special features and brand new additions!   Designed for even the pickiest of buyers, there are 3 generous sized bedrooms on the main level a sunny large living room with easy access to the new kitchen - a great entertaining space.  The hardwood flooring is absolutely beautiful throughout the home.  The kitchen has contemporary styled, soft-close, cabinetry with quartz countertops and come with all the stainless steel appliances.   Both of bathrooms have been modernized with floor-to-ceiling eye-catching tile, floating vanities, exclusive fixtures and more. The lower level offers an additional bedroom, the amazing new and full bathroom, a laundry room and the family room which is breathtaking it has a custom built entertainment wall unit complete with a built-in fireplace. Outside leads to a fully fenced in yard w/ privacy fence, 2 car garage w/ duel access service doors and attached covered patio area. Easy access to public transportation, expressway, restaurants, shopping and other area conveniences. Come take a look...
